{
 "name": "RPlog_Blood_Brothers",
 "title": "Blood Brothers",
 "summary": "Former StarOps pilot Drax Rendolen uses an old code from his Knights of Korriban days to summon the veteran smuggler Krackor Reincus to a hidden oasis in an asteroid field near Corellia, docking the Arcadia to Krackor's black ILC Edgecrusher. Over drinks and cigaras the two old associates catch up and discover they share a deep scar: both were grotesquely violated by the Sith Lord Malign, who infused his own genetic code into them. Drax explains he is worried about Andreya Carvalo, a woman he cares for who has gone off on a reckless solo vendetta, and he needs the destination where Krackor dropped her. They strike a deal, Drax trading a cache of Durindfire gems and a New Republic customs and intelligence connection for the answer, and Krackor reveals he took her to the Imperial-held world of Coruscant. Parting as brothers, Drax sets off to arrange his own insertion onto Coruscant to find her.",
